text:
You were singing...
Was it the song for the next stage?

Ah, it's fine.
I'm not blaming you.

...It's a song I like right now.
When I sing it, I get all sorts of ideas...

I'm hoping those ideas
can help with the next song.

I see...
so it's for the stage after all.

If you don't mind,
I'd like to hear that song.

You might get better advice that way...
but it's a bit embarrassing...
